init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is a story of the end of the world, and the beginning of the next.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: John was now in his final year of school, and was one of the stronger students.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was a tall, well-built young man with short brown hair and a friendly face.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "John, we have some good news for you," his father said.
